description:
English translation of the Japanese manga UQ Holder! (ユーキューホルダー!).

A brand new series from Ken Akamatsu (Love Hina, Negima!). Set in the far future of the world of Negima!, it will draw in older Negima! fans. But it is also an entirely new story, so new fans will enjoy it as well. Negi Springfield, the boy wizard of the hit manga Negima!, fought and won many battles. Now it is decades later and Negi's grandson, a little boy name Touta, dreams of leaving his quiet village and heading to the City. But first he must defeat his teacher, the immortal vampire Evangeline!
name: UQ Holder!
